:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
exam_data <- read_csv("data/Exam_data.csv")
```
:::


## Box plot as a contrast with more detailed visual representations from class



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(data = exam_data,
       aes(x = ENGLISH,
           y = CLASS)) +
  geom_boxplot()
```
